\v 7 But I’ll have mercy on Yehudah’s \add descendants\add*, and I’ll save them \add so they’ll be able to see that it was\add* their God Yahweh. (I won’t save them using \add bows, swords, battles\add*, horses, or horsemen.)”
\p
\v 8 After she’d weaned Lo-Ruhamah, she got pregnant \add again\add* and bore a \add second\add* son.
